OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FCouncil leader Cllr Liam Robinson,
OL,8,Fpart of a new leadership team at the
OL,9,Fhelm of the authority, said: "I am
OL,10,Freally pleased that the government has
OL,11,Faccepted the recommendations of the
OL,12,Fcommissioners and confirmed the
OL,13,Fhanding back of some powers to the
OL,14,Fcouncil ahead of schedule.
OL,16,F"It is recognition of the fact that we
OL,17,Fhave made significant progress over
OL,18,Fthe last nine months or so, although
OL,19,Fwe know that we have much more to do."
