OL,4,Csome powers three years after damning
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe government today confirmed there
OL,8,Fwill be a "significant reduction" in
OL,9,Fthe intervention at with revised
OL,10,Fdirections being published
OL,12,FThe council may now appoint most
OL,13,Fsenior managers again and it will
OL,14,Fregain oversight of the finance and
OL,15,Fhighways functions from 31 March.
OL,17,FThe size of the commissioner team will
OL,18,Freduce from five to four, with members
OL,19,Fsteadily reducing their involvement
OL,20,Fand days spent with the council.
