OL,3,CLiverpool City Council handed back
OL,4,Csome powers three years after damning
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FCllr Robinson said he has held
OL,8,Fconstructive discussions with the
OL,9,Flocal government minister, Simon Hoare
OL,10,FMP, about the intervention.
OL,12,FThe minister has written to the
OL,13,Fcouncil leader to say the government
OL,14,Frecognises the progress made and
OL,15,Fwishes "to support a managed
OL,16,Ftransition to ending the statutory
OL,17,Fintervention".
OL,19,FCllr Robinson added, "I am confident
OL,20,Fthis marks the beginning of the end of
OL,21,Fthe intervention as we know it.
